01:18:48.239 --> 01:18:50.239 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Proszę pani!

01:18:50.359 --> 01:18:52.359 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Proszę. Dla Jana.

01:18:53.680 --> 01:18:56.760 line:85% position:50% size:80%
